## ⚙️ .gitattributes

**Download:** [.gitattributes](sandbox:///mnt/agents/output/.gitattributes)

```gitattributes
# Force C++ as the primary detected language
# Hide non-code files from GitHub language statistics

# C++ source files - force detectable
*.cpp linguist-detectable=true
*.h linguist-detectable=true
*.hpp linguist-detectable=true
*.c linguist-detectable=true

# Documentation - excluded from language stats
*.md linguist-documentation
LICENSE linguist-documentation
CHANGELOG linguist-documentation
CONTRIBUTING linguist-documentation

# Compiled binaries - generated (excluded)
*.exe linguist-generated
*.out linguist-generated
*.o linguist-generated
*.obj linguist-generated
*.dll linguist-generated
*.so linguist-generated
*.a linguist-generated
*.lib linguist-generated

# Build files - vendored (excluded)
Makefile linguist-vendored
CMakeLists.txt linguist-vendored
cmake_install.cmake linguist-vendored

# IDE files - vendored (excluded)
.vscode/* linguist-vendored
.idea/* linguist-vendored
*.sln linguist-vendored
*.vcxproj linguist-vendored
